    "Update your training paces to match?" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "要更新訓練配速來搭配嗎？"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Use the stepper to adjust. Changes only commit when you tap Save." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "用步進器調整。按下「儲存」後才會生效。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "VDOT improved" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "VDOT 提升了"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "VDOT is a number that represents your current running fitness, developed by coach Jack Daniels. It is calculated from a recent race result and reflects the effective VO₂max you demonstrated on race day." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "VDOT 是代表你目前跑步體能的數字，由 Jack Daniels 教練提出。它從近期的比賽成績推算而來，反映你比賽當天實際展現的 VO₂max。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "We can swap today's hard session for an easy 5 km run." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "我們可以把今天的高強度訓練換成 5 公里的輕鬆跑。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
